title: 12/31/21 DPS Hour 2 Rob Parker & TJ Houshmandzadeh talk Russell Wilson’s Future
itunes:title: 12/31/21 DPS Hour 2 Rob Parker & TJ Houshmandzadeh talk Russell Wilson’s Future
description:
Rob & TJ wonder where Seahawks QB Russell Wilson may play next year after the QB is non-committal on his future in Seattle, and what team might be the best fit if he plays elsewhere. Which NFL teams are facing a must win game this weekend, highlighted by the Arizona Cardinals desperately needing a win against the Dallas Cowboys!
